unittitle_ssm: New York Metro Area Postal Union Records
abstract_ssm: The New York Metro Area Postal Union (American Postal Workers Union, Local 10) represents clerks, motor vehicle staff, maintenance workers and mail-handlers in the great New York City area. The collection includes minutes, administrative files, officers files, stewards files, bargaining files, grievances, affiliates files, publications of the local, reports, financial records, subject files, archived websites, and ephemera.
